               <p>Cross-examined by MR. ADOLPHUS. Q. At what time did you go in to possession? - A. Between seven and eight o'clock in the evening; Phillips, the sheriff's officer, employed me; I did not desire the prisoner to go to Phillips, nor deliver him a letter.</p>
