            , clerk to Messrs. Stevens and Co., solicitors, proved the service of a notice on the prisoner to produce on his trial the note in question.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-85-person881">
                  RICHARD 
                  RAY
               <interp inst="t18290409-85-person881" type="surname" value="RAY"></interp>
