            . I am a clerk in the Sun Fire-office. The prisoner came to the office on the day of the fire, and asked if his policies were ready - I told him they would be signed in a day or two, and then sent.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-85-person884">
                  PETER 
                  CHARLES HUME
               <interp inst="t18290409-85-person884" type="surname" value="CHARLES HUME"></interp>
